  "title": "fix(insights): detect clicks on children of [data-insights] HTML elements",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nWhen the insights integration is used in the following way:\r\n\r\n```js\r\n<a href=\"#\" ${insights('clickObjectIDsAfterSearch', {...})}>\r\n   <h1> ${hit.name} </h1>\r\n</a>\r\n```\r\nand click occurs on `h1`, insight client is not called.\r\n\r\nThis PR addresses this problem.\r\n",
